{"tid":2054094,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[八日維新] CCTV: “地攤經濟”不能一哄而起","createTime":"2020-06-07T00:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T02:53:15.000Z","uid":128923,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d5d5cf511b68ed0a96b8f4f39429fde528d20db4","tid":2054094,"uid":128923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T00:54:01.000Z","msg":"//當前，&ldquo;地攤經濟&rdquo;在一些地方熱鬧起來，這固然有其生存發展的價值，但並非包治百病的靈丹妙藥。不同的城市有不同的定位，也有不同的發展階段，一旦脫離實際，一哄而起、盲目跟風，就會適得其反，&ldquo;蠶食&rdquo;來之不易的治理成果。<br />\n<br />\n城市治理也如同烹小鮮，必須精準施策，用心用情。特別是對於北京、上海、廣州這樣的特大型城市而言，精細化管理方是正道。目前，各大一線城市均未盲目跟風，也沒有發布所謂&ldquo;地攤地圖&rdquo;，一些城市更明確對亂擺攤說不。這是清醒的。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.news.cctv.com/2020/06/07/ARTILFxj7qKmVbehNgGQWrOl200607.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.news.cctv.com%2F2020%2F06%2F07%2FARTILFxj7qKmVbehNgGQWrOl200607.shtml&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUl3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=00df62a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.news.cctv.com/2020/06/07/ARTILFxj7qKmVbehNgGQWrOl200607.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df80657ff69468379880dc0338603df8f37330a","tid":2054094,"uid":128923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T00:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yJsuKmk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyJsuKmk.jpg&h=0c0384ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1d8fcb16c8c3bd1f8af72e405dc75b154bb1872","tid":2054094,"uid":33848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T00:55:15.000Z","msg":"強仔真係廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf11bc542641949ea